{"tid":728051,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"notebook打機過熱","createTime":"2018-07-03T13:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T16:06:46.000Z","uid":35693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2115394fa956caebb99cab6258a7bdfc8260fc31","tid":728051,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"首先我都知買notebook黎打機係on9我認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但屋企細無位，我買notebook又可以拎返工做野<br />\n<br />\n我用緊Acer nitro 5<br />\n7代i7 16gb ram 1050ti 果個spec<br />\n玩Gta睇到粒u徘徊係七八十度，<br />\n有時會上到九十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知notebook散熱係差<br />\n但呢個係咪一個好唔正常既溫度呢？<br />\n<br />\n部機有個內置既軟件叫coolboost<br />\n話開左會散熱好啲但我已經次次都開<br />\n都上到八十幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我上一部macbook pro都用左5年<br />\n如果呢部acer頂到3年我都覺得賺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e973da706d496b4b2a279b03a7488951ce75f976","tid":728051,"uid":32577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"acer用到一年冇壞已經算好彩"},{"pid":"b006708bf5797b9abac2478246e34d8768340b0d","tid":728051,"uid":162695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"acer差唔多啦"},{"pid":"0a10618616bce209b675686bb0e4ec7eeaede414","tid":728051,"uid":65023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:19:52.000Z","msg":"90度以下都叫正常溫度，用ThrottleStop 降volt試下可能低幾度"},{"pid":"782601341f91ae2c3afba13575ed1c870f8721d0","tid":728051,"uid":112434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"Acer長期full load燒機95度用咗一年"},{"pid":"ba1202bfb7889f5827ec31af42e90d474e8c74a4","tid":728051,"