1a43b9034b24d3c200a6fef04a49a6a861ab","tid":728051,"uid":191717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"intel xtu降壓 低5-10度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"其實安唔安全架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電腦智識我真係好有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係邊玩邊學緊..."},{"pid":"c47a68d3b64bf13ff33d09ab72649851f0c0da84","tid":728051,"uid":65023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"真心怕既就降頻啦<br />\nDownload個 Throttlestop<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.Disable Turbo = 關左個boost佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/225124_64befa18637bf0cb5338cecd2e1b0d5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F225124_64befa18637bf0cb5338cecd2e1b0d5c.png&h=18b9148c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.入FIVR，降CPU同Cache電壓-125mv 叫做 stable.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/225415_0ff0a3d73e6d6aa1d6deddaa9fdde263.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F225415_0ff0a3d73e6d6aa1d6deddaa9fdde263.png&h=189deb3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.入game開v-sync lock死fps60...FPS唔過60可以比GPU佢留力...<br />\n<br />\nPS. 想lock死最高就開SpeedShift即係新既Speedstep，0最高 255最低，唔係勁game唔使開盡...用default<br />\n用之前要入TPL開左佢先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/225853_2d5ae404ca714ec7b16c97e3cc1b2de3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F225853_2d5ae404ca714ec7b16c97e3cc1b2de3.png&h=f3c75634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nXTU同一原理"},{"pid":"09ef7202a19c86c07299559057aca2cbe6ad1195","tid":728051,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47a68d3b64bf13ff33d09ab72649851f0c0da84","tid":728051,"uid":65023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"真心怕既就降頻啦<br />\nDownload個 Throttlestop<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.Disable Turbo = 關左個boost佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/225124_64befa18637bf0cb5338cecd2e1b0d5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F225124_64befa18637bf0cb5338cecd2e1b0d5c.png&h=18b9148c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.入FIVR，降CPU同Cache電壓-125mv 叫做 stable.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/225415_0ff0a3d73e6d6aa1d6deddaa9fdde263.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F225415_0ff0a3d73e6d6aa1d6deddaa9fdde263.png&h=189deb3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.入game開v-sync lock死fps60...FPS唔過60可以比GPU佢留力...<br />\n<br />\nPS. 想lock死最高就開SpeedShift即係新既Speedstep，0最高 255最低，唔係勁game唔使開盡...用default<br />\n用之前要入TPL開左佢先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/225853_2d5ae404ca714ec7b16c97e3cc1b2de3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F225853_2d5ae404ca714ec7b16c97e3cc1b2de3.png&h=f3c75634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nXTU同一原理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒巴打，我研究下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9d90ed75f32bed75936e6eaefbf05a201bd359","tid":728051,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd82633237126e0dad2ae5bc567119da993b5c76","tid":728051,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0